h3 Toolbar Tabs

p Tabs can also be included above toolbars (any toolbar variation - default or primary) using the following structure.
p Toolbar tabs are useful as a high-level filter - altering the perspective on the same (or closely related) dataset, functionality or presentation.

.component
  .row.toolbar-tabs
    .col-xs-12
      ul.nav.nav-tabs
        li.active
          a href='#toolbar-tabs-kame' data-toggle='tab' Kame
        li
          a href='#toolbar-tabs-hame' data-toggle='tab' Hame
        li
          a href='#toolbar-tabs-haaa' data-toggle='tab' Haaa
  .row
    .col-xs-12
      .toolbar.toolbar-default
        .container-fluid
          .row
            .col-xs-12
              .btn.btn-default Default

pre
  code.slim
    | .row.toolbar-tabs
        .col-xs-12
          ul.nav.nav-tabs
            li.active
              a href='#tabs' data-toggle='tab'
                = 'title 1'
            li
              a href='#tabs' data-toggle='tab'
                = 'title 2'
